quran[44]{c,v,t}:
  23,75,"Ama koros keenih Racmatneeh, qabar kee qululuk keenil tanim fayya keenik hayinninoy koroosannuu kee sinni caddok taturut amo ayxeerak yenen badit kee agay-waagat anuk"
  23,76,"Kaadu nummah digaalah ken nibbixeeh, ken mokkorrek, tokkel usun sinni Rabbih Rammitaah kaat xaaqima mara makkinnon"
  23,77,Akeeral gibdi digaala-le afa keenil fakna waqdi usun too waqdi ummaan kayrik inkih yabboodeenih
  23,78,"Usuk Yalla kinni aytiitaa kee intiitaay sorkocobaxitte siinih gintem, isin aniqmatal Yalla faatittaanam siinik dagoh"
  23,79,"Kaadu Yalla kinni sinaamey baaxô bagul sin gintem, kaadu rabteeniik gamadal kaâ fanah maagowtan cisab kee galtoh"
  23,80,"Kaadu Yalla kinni suge waytik sin gintaah sin taynuwweeh sin qiddam, kaadu bar kee laqo ittal abta ciggiiliyya usuk leeh kay taama kinnik isin amahal makaskassowtaanaa"
  23,81,"Kinnih immay ama koros rabak wadir mano tanim manummaysinnaay, naharsi koros kah itte innah itte"
  23,82,"Rabneeh burtaay, lafoofi nakke waqdi, diggah nanu nammeyhaak nanuwweeh ugtennoo iyyen"
  23,83,"Nummah nee kee ni-abbobti amahah dumaak xagnisimne, amah tu-hinna naharsi marih diroobaa kee hayyayyoona akke waytek iyyen"
  23,84,Nabiyow baaxoo kee teetil tanim iyyi leeh iyyi gineeh Yaaxige mara tekkeenik keenik ixxic
  23,85,"Yalli tet gineeh, is Yallih iimi axcelon, toysa Yalli rabak sarra sin ugusuwaamih duddalem makassittaanaa? Keenik ixxic"
  23,86,Nabiyow malcina Qaraanih Rabbi miyyaay? Ķaxxa Qarshih Rabbi miyyaay? keenik ixxic
  23,87,"Yalli ken gineeh, usun Yallih iimi axcelon, toysa Yallih digaalák mamceesittaanaa? Kaak kalihim taqbuden waqdi keenik ixxic"
  23,88,"Nabiyow ummaanimih reeda iyyi leeh? Ummaanimih kadnooni iyyin gabat taniih?Ķaadu usuk (Yalla kinnuk) wadu faxxam wadaah, Usuk digaalá kah faxa mara kaak waddaah cattam matan, woh yaaxige mara tekkeenik keenik ixxic"
  23,89,"Usun kol gacisak:Reeda inkih Yallih iimi axce-lon, toysa Yalla inkittossaanaah taqbudeenimik mannal daggawtaanaa makkottaanaa? kaak kalihim taqbuden waqdi baab abeyni baab siinil abeh innah keenik ixxicx"
  23,90,"Wonna hinnay Qhuraan cakkil keenih bahne, kaadu diggah usun dirableela Yallat agleyta haanam kee Rabi lakat ugut yanim yangaddeenimil"
  23,91,"Yalli hebeltô baxa isi nafsih mahaysitinnaay, kaadu kalah qibaadá cakkisita Yalli kaâ luk mayan, aka Yalli kaâ luk suginnay, toysa kulli Yalli isi ginó haysitak yeneeh, gari-garu keenik korisak yeneeh, aamuk yenen addunyah amoytiitih innah, Yalli koros kaa edde weelossu haytaamak saytunnooweh"
  23,92,"Yalli isi ginók qellittam kee tambulleem inkih yaaxigi kinni, tokkel Yalli agleh kaat hayya haanamak fayya iyyeeh, saytunnooweh"
  23,93,"Ixxic Nabiyow:yi-Rabbow ama koros addunyal digaalák kah xagnisimtem yoo taybullu waytek, keenî luk yoo mafinqisin"
  23,94,Toysa Yi-Rabbow daalimiinih yan maray finqitê loowot yoo mahaysin
  23,95,Kaadu Nabiyow nanu diggah digaalák ken kah xagnisnem koo naybulleemih dudda-lino
  23,96,"Nabiyow ku-naqboytit umam kol bahtek ken umaane maqaaney aysuk raqtat gutuqaay ken umaanel ken makataatin, nanu usun dirab kee anqasay kol abaana Naaxigehik"
  23,97,Kaadu Nabiyow yi-Rabbow sheetoonâ waswasak Koo maggansita ixxic
  23,98,Kaadu yi-Rabbow sheetoona yi -caagidit yolluk martaah Yolluk tangaleemik koo maggansita ixxic
  23,99,Korosuk numuk teynah Rabi yamaate waqdi yi-Rabbow addunyâ fanah yoo gacis iyya nadaamitak
  23,100,"limaan kee meqe taamay addunyal cabeeh bayse abamkeh yoo gacis iyya, aleey addunyâ fanih madaara matan, diggah is Qangaray usuk edde yaabay tu-kaah xiqe wayta kinni, kaadu keenik foocal reebuy addunyah gacaanamak ken waasa yan edde ugsumoonu waan ayrô (Qhiyaamah ayrò kinnuk) fanah kaal elle sugaanaah"
  23,101,"Baantá fuxsumta waqdi (Qhiyaamah ayró kinnuk), toysa too ayro ken fanat Ramaddiini maraaqaay, mariiy mara keenik messera ken geya gibdaabinih sabbatah"
  23,102,"Maqaane kak temeggeeh, meqe taamah miidaan kak yiqilsee mari cisab keenik aban waqdi, toysa woo mari usun Jannatal yoffoofe mara (limaye mara) kinnon"
  23,103,"Kaadu meqe taamah miidaan kak daggooweeh, uma taamah miidaan kak yiqilsee mari, toysa woo mari sinni nafsi finqiseeh kasaarise maray Jahannam giráh addal waara kinnon"
  23,104,"Ken foocitte gira carrissaah, usun tet addal foocitte cibbihaanaah gira carrisse arroobuk moddin keenik amballuk Raqqa iyya"
  23,105,"Yalli keenik iyyah: Yi-Qhuraanih aayoota addunyal siinil ankirriyimak masuginnaa? tokkel isin tet dirabboysak sugteenik"
  23,106,"Ni-Rabbow ni-umaanee kee ni- nafsi fayxi nek teyseeh, addunyal cakki gitak makkoote marah sugne iyyan"
  23,107,"Ni-Rabbow girak nee eyyeeqaay, addunyâ fanah nee gacis, tokkel nanu koroosannuu kee umaaneh gacnek, toysa nanu diggah ninni nafsi koroosannut yudlume mara akkennok iyyan"
  23,108,"Dira! Tet addal (gira kinnuk) daffeyaay, Yol luk mayaabina keenik iyya Yalli"
  23,109,"Diggah yi-naqoosak Buttay moominiinih tani Ni-Rabbow neemenehik dambi neh cabaay, neh Racmat atu Racmatta leemik inkih Racmattah yayse Rabbi kinnitok axcuk sugte"
  23,110,"Tokkel isin anqasah ken (moominiin kinnuk) haysitten, keenil abtan anqasat gabxitten Yallih cusiyya hawwenni haytaanam fanah, sinni koroosannut edde Raqteeniih addunyal anqsah keenil asaaluk sugten"
  23,111,"Diggah asaaku Anu Yi-naqoosak tama teemene butta jannatal ken galta, sin adaa kee Yallih taaqatal yisbireenimih sabbatah, diggah usun Jannatal yaffoofe mara (limaye mara) yekken"
  23,112,"Korosuk girah addal yanin waqdi, Addunyal Baaxô Bagul liggiditteh ixxuk magide sugteeniih keenik axcuk ken essera Yalli"
  23,113,"Meesiiy digaalâ gibdah sabbatah ayrooy, hinnay ayrók garab sugnek alsittee kee ayroorâ loowo diggi haa mara esser iyyan"
  23,114,"Isin Addunyal tu-masuginniton dago wakti akke waytek, addunyal sugteenih gide Yallih taaqatal asbirinnitoonuy jannatal affoofak tenen, diggah isin woh yaaxige marah suginnitoonuy keenik iyye Yalli"
  23,115,Sinaamey cagalah digir kee cantalbakah sin ginnem tekkeleenii? Kaadu diggah isin Nee fan aduure waytaanaah gacsime waytaanam tekkeleenii cisab kee galtoh akeeral
  23,116,"Yalli fayya iyyeeh saytunnooweh, usuk cakki amoyta kinni tu digirih ginaamak, Kaak sa qibaadá cakkisita Yalli mayan, meqe Qarshiy nabâ Rabbi kinni"
  23,117,"Yallâ luk aka Yalla yaqbude num aka Yalli Qibaada cakkisitaamih sumaq mali, toysa cagalah kay uma taamah galtó kay Rabbih xaqul tan akeeral, diggah koroosite mari affaf mali Qhiyaamah ayró"
  23,118,"Nabiyow:Yi-Rabbow dambi yoh cabaay yoh Racmat, kaadu Atu Racmatta leemik Racmattah yayse Rabbi kinnitok ixxic"